@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (tmp - v2)
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.25) + ((v1 + 0.68 - v2 + 0.19) / v1))
    v1 = 0.09
    v0 = 0.43
    v1 = v2
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.12) * wp.abs(v1 + 0.19)) - 0.21)
    tmp = 0.79
    data[tid] = v0
